songs.title: The Good Life
songs.lyrics:
[Verse]
It's the good life
Full of fun, seems to be the ideal
Yes, the good life
Let's you hide all the sadness you feel
You won't really fall in love 'cause you can't take the chance
So be honest with yourself, don't try to fake romance
Yes, the good life, to be free and explore the unknown
Like the heartaches when you learn you must face them alone

[Outro]
Please remember I still want you and in case you wonder why
Well, just wake up, kiss that good life
Goodbye (Oh)
Please remember I still want you and in case you wonder why
Well, just wake up, kiss that good life
Goodbye (Oh)
